 {"id":"bd-btg9","title":"Implement test results formatter","description":"## Task: Test Results Formatter

### Parent Feature
Phase 3: Advanced Output Components (bd-1lkf)

### Overview
Create a beautiful test results display with pass/fail indicators, timing, grouping, and summary statistics that enhances developer experience during test runs.

### Background & Reasoning
Test output is one of the most frequently viewed outputs in development. Beautiful test results:
- Make it immediately obvious which tests passed/failed
- Help locate failures quickly through visual hierarchy
- Provide motivation through satisfying green checkmarks
- Show timing to identify slow tests
- Give progress feedback during long test suites

### Technical Implementation

#### Data Structures
```rust
// crates/fastapi-output/src/components/test_results.rs

pub struct TestResult {
    pub name: String,
    pub module_path: String,
    pub status: TestStatus,
    pub duration: Duration,
    pub failure_message: Option<String>,
    pub failure_diff: Option<(String, String)>, // (expected, actual)
}

pub enum TestStatus {
    Passed,
    Failed,
    Skipped,
    Ignored,
}

pub struct TestSuite {
    pub name: String,
    pub results: Vec<TestResult>,
    pub total_duration: Duration,
}

pub struct TestResultsDisplay {
    suites: Vec<TestSuite>,
    show_timing: bool,
    show_passed: bool,  // Sometimes hide passed to focus on failures
    group_by_module: bool,
}
```

#### Visualization

**Rich Mode (Full Display)**:
```
┌─────────────────── Test Results ───────────────────┐
│                                                     │
│ tests::unit::parser                                 │
│   ✓ test_parse_method ........................ 2ms │
│   ✓ test_parse_path .......................... 1ms │
│   ✓ test_parse_headers ...................... 15ms │
│   ✗ test_parse_body .......................... 3ms │
│     │ Expected: Content-Type: application/json     │
│     │ Actual:   Content-Type: text/plain           │
│                                                     │
│ tests::integration::routing                         │
│   ✓ test_basic_route ........................ 45ms │
│   ✓ test_parameterized_route ................ 52ms │
│   ⊘ test_websocket_route ................ skipped │
│                                                     │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Summary                                             │
│ ████████████████████████░░░░ 85% (17/20)           │
│                                                     │
│ ✓ Passed:  17    Duration: 1.23s                   │
│ ✗ Failed:   2    Slowest:  test_db_connection 892ms│
│ ⊘ Skipped:  1                                       │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Plain Mode (CI-friendly)**:
```
